title: Maria Kobylińska
text: Maria Kobylińska (born 2 February 1960) is a Polish <a href="rowing%20%28sport%29">rower</a>. She competed in the <a href="Rowing%20at%20the%201980%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%20quadruple%20sculls">women's quadruple sculls</a> event at the <a href="1980%20Summer%20Olympics">1980 Summer Olympics</a>.
